  "keyFeatures": [
    "RTMP publish and playback with FMLE-compatible authentication",
    "SRT protocol support (caller, listener, rendezvous modes)",
    "WHIP/WHEP WebRTC streaming (alpha)",
    "MoQT protocol support (alpha)",
    "Multi-camera capture via AVCaptureMultiCamSession",
    "Video mixing with overlays, watermarks, and text via ScreenObjects",
    "Audio mixing with multi-track support",
    "ReplayKit and ScreenCaptureKit screen capture support",
    "Swift strict concurrency (async/await) compliance",
    "Enhanced RTMP support (HEVC, OPUS)",
    "MTHKView and PiPHKView for video rendering",
    "StreamSession unified API across protocols"
  ],
